			<h6 style="text-align:center;">Athletic&nbsp;Programs</h6>
			<p style="text-align: center;">Each year over 1,000 youth participate in The Salvation Army of Wake County&nbsp;Athletics Programs, learning the importance of team play and good sportsmanship. Always maintaining a Christ-centered atmosphere, there are pre-game devotions and prayers for each sport. Here, children are taught that winning means having fun, learning fundamental skills, and being a part of a team where they make&nbsp;a difference.&nbsp;For more information contact our Youth Programs at <a href="tel:919-832-6918" target="">919-832-6918</a>.</p>
<p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-center" style="text-align: center;"><a class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2" href="https://goo.gl/maps/NCDkf2KboE2buetaA">Directions</a></p>
			<div class="my-2"></div>
			<div class="my-2"></div>
			<div class="my-2"></div>
			<div class="rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-secondary-200 text-light" style="color:red;font-weight:bold">
<h3><span style="color: #fffffff;">Soccer</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-size: 24px; color: red;">Registration is now open!</span></p>
<ul>
<li>All coaches, assistants, and players must register. The cost is $157 per player</li>
<li style="font-weight: bold;"><strong>Registration will close on July 17, 2026 @11:59 PM</strong></li>
<li>10-week program from August 3, 2026, through October 6, 2026</li>
<li>All leagues are for boys and girls
<ul>
<li>4-year-old league</li>
<li>5-6-year-old league</li>
<li>7-8-year-old league</li>
<li>9-11-year-old league</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>All coaches, assistants, and players must register</li>
<li>Shin guards and cleats are required</li>
<li>Practices will start the week of August 3, 2026 (scheduled on weekdays based on coach availability)</li>
<li>Games will start the week of August 24, 2026</li>
<li>A Christ-centered atmosphere is maintained in our pre-game devotions and prayers for each sport</li>
</ul>
<p>During registration, there is an opportunity to make a donation to the Hurley Raynor Community Fund, which helps provide scholarships to deserving youth and helps us maintain our facility. This fund honors Coach Hurley Raynor, who has coached two generations of community center families.</p>
<p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-start"><a class="btn btn-light gap-1 mt-2" href="https://www.easyreg.org/cgi-bin/acct/UIVWDBCZX4/displayForm.pl?dir=QD7WWZIT_2026">Coach Registration </a><a class="btn btn-light gap-1 mt-2" href="https://www.easyreg.org/cgi-bin/acct/UIVWDBCZX4/displayForm.pl?dir=NM2X27NR_2026">Player Registration</a></p>
</div>
			<div class="my-2"></div>
			<div class="py-5"></div>
			<div class="rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-secondary-200 text-light" style="color:#FFFFFF">
<h3>"Nooners" Adult Basketball</h3>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Often referred to as the "Nooners", adults will gather at The Salvation Army's Community Center to play pick-up games. There is no official league - just fun fellowship &amp; basketball. Please know that we will have to close the gym from time to time due to special events going on in the gym. We will try to give you advanced notice when those events occur.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>Overview</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">Registration is required</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">January 5&nbsp;- December 13, 2025</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">Monday, Wednesday, and Friday 11:30 - 1:30 pm</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">Guests are welcome for a one-time fee of $10.00</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">Must be 18+ years of age</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">A Christ-centered atmosphere is maintained in our gym, so please act accordingly</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>Fees</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">Option 1. Pay $10 each time you come</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">Option 2.&nbsp;Pay $50 for a 12-visit pass (to be used only in 2025)</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">Option 3.&nbsp;Pay $200 for a yearlong pass (good for all of 2025)</span></li>
</ul>
<p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-start"><a class="btn btn-light gap-1 mt-2" href="https://www.easyreg.org/cgi-bin/acct/UIVWDBCZX4/displayForm.pl?dir=9UZOCDC5_2023" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Register</a></p>
</div>
