<h3>Winter Youth Basketball</h3>
<p>Get ready to dribble, shoot, and score with us in an action-packed season of fun and teamwork!</p>
<p>Season dates: January 5, 2026 - March 13, 2026. The cost is $157 per player.</p>
<p><strong>Overview:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Coach and player registration is required</li>
<li>Coach registration is NOW OPEN</li>
<li>Player&nbsp;registration is NOW OPEN&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>
<li>Ages - 5 -14 (boys &amp; girls)</li>
<li>Practices start Monday, January 5, 2026
<ul>
<li>Tuesdays (ages 5-6)</li>
<li>Wednesdays (ages 7-8)</li>
<li>Thursdays (ages 9-11 and 12-14)</li>
<li>Fridays (ages 12-14)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Games&nbsp;start date: Tuesday, January 26, 2026</li>
</ul>
<p>A Christ-centered atmosphere is maintained in our pre-game devotions and prayers for each sport.</p>
<p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-start"><a class="btn btn-light gap-1 mt-2" href="https://www.easyreg.org/cgi-bin/acct/UIVWDBCZX4/displayForm.pl?dir=3M1FK1NM_2025">Coach Registration</a><a class="btn btn-light gap-1 mt-2" href="https://www.easyreg.org/cgi-bin/acct/UIVWDBCZX4/displayForm.pl?dir=75FJISNT_2025" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Player Register</a></p>
</div>
