<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">Practices will start the week of March 16, 2026&nbsp;(scheduled on weekdays based on coach availability)</span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">Games will start the week of April 6, 2026 (scheduled on weekdays based&nbsp;on coach availability)</span></li>
