</ul>
<p><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">Pitching machine (9-12&nbsp;years of age)</span></strong></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">Practices will start the week of March 16,&nbsp;2026&nbsp;(scheduled on weekdays based on coach availability)</span></span></li>
