<h3><span style="tab-stops: list .5in;">Open Gym</span></h3>
<p><strong><span style="tab-stops: list .5in;">Please note:</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="tab-stops: list .5in;">Our Open Gym membership gives you unlimited access to pickup basketball and pickleball for the entire month. With your membership, checking in is simple and hassle-free.</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="tab-stops: list .5in;">Memberships are valid only for the month in which they are purchased. ($5 per day for non-members)</span></li>
<li><span style="tab-stops: list .5in;">Renewals are required monthly to continue participation</span></li>
<li><span style="tab-stops: list .5in;">Cost is $38 ($35 Flat rate + $3 PayPal surcharge)</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="tab-stops: list .5in;">We’re excited to have you join us and hope you enjoy everything our Open Gym program has to offer!<br></span></p>
<p>Pickleball: Thursdays 3-6 p.m.&amp;nbsp;(Will add days as participation grows)</p>
<p>Basketball: Monday, Wednesday, Friday 11:30 a.m. - 1:30 p.m.</p>
<p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-start"><a class="btn btn-light gap-1 mt-2" href="https://www.easyreg.org/cgi-bin/acct/UIVWDBCZX4/displayForm.pl?dir=YSXDONY4_2025">Registration</a></p>
</div>
